[0.4, "o", "\u001b[36m*\u001b[0m \u001b[33mI see a problem you haven't thought about.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.3, "o", "You said \"enter your name\" — but what if someone opens\r\n"]
[0.3, "o", "the link from a different browser? They lose their identity.\r\n"]
[0.6, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.4, "o", "\u001b[33mMy recommendation:\u001b[0m Unique member URL per person.\r\n"]
[0.3, "o", "app.com/map/abc123/member/xyz — the URL IS the identity.\r\n"]
